%section#wv-community
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-lg-7
        %h1 life groups
        %p Our Life Groups are at the heart of our church. They meet in people's homes in Winchester and the surrounding areas. They are a great place to get to know others, share both the big and the small things of life, and learn to do the things Jesus did.
        %p Groups run on a termly basis, with some groups lasting just a term and other groups lasting longer. You are welcome to continue going to the same group for several terms.

        %h2 how to join a life group
        = haml :_group_blurb, locals: { term: @term }

        %p
          %a.btn.btn-primary{:href => '/lifegroups'} View the list of life groups &raquo;
      #flickr.hidden-xs.hidden-sm.col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        %img{:src => "/images/photos/areas/community/life-group.jpg"}
        %img{:src => "/images/photos/areas/community/family-fun-day.jpg"}
        %img{:src => "/images/photos/areas/community/quiz-night.jpg"}

- FOUR_WEEKS = 60 * 60 * 24 * 28
- groups = @talks.partition {|t| t.date > Time.now - FOUR_WEEKS}
%section#wv-talks
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        .wv-caption
          %h1 talk downloads
          %p We record every talk we give on Sunday, and a number of the talks that are delivered during the week and at special events.
          %p
            %strong Within the last month
        .row#wv-talks-within-last-month
          - groups.first.each do |talk|
